OL,7,FSignificant IT issues have forced
OL,8,Fambulance diversions and appointment
OL,9,Fcancellations at hospitals in the
OL,10,FSouthern Trust area.
OL,12,FDaisy Hill Hospital in Newry and
OL,13,FCraigavon Area Hospital are among the
OL,14,Ftrust facilitates affected.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the Southern Health
OL,17,Fand Social Care Trust said it is
OL,18,Fprioritising emergency and critical
OL,19,Fcare patients.
