OL,7,FIt urged any other patients to avoid
OL,8,Fcoming to any of its hospitals until
OL,9,Ffurther notice.
OL,11,F"The trust is currently experiencing
OL,12,Fsignificant issues with our IT systems
OL,13,Fwhich are having an impact on our
OL,14,Fservices," it said.
OL,16,F"Ambulance diverts have been put in
OL,17,Fplace whilst work continues to further
OL,18,Finvestigate and resolve the issues.
OL,20,F"We are prioritising emergency and
OL,21,Fcritically ill patients at this time.
