OL,7,F"Any other patients should not come to
OL,8,Ftheir appointments at any hospital or
OL,9,Fcommunity services today until further
OL,10,Fnotice.
OL,12,F"We ask that people avoid coming to
OL,13,Four hospitals and other sites, but
OL,14,Fvisiting a patient is still possible.
OL,15,FFurther updates will be provided in
OL,16,Fdue course."
OL,18,FSDLP health spokesman Colin McGrath
OL,19,Fexpressed concern.
