OL,7,F"While the details of what has
OL,8,Fhappened will cause understandable
OL,9,Fconcern, it is essential that the
OL,10,Ftrust work to reassure the public,"
OL,11,Fsaid the South Down MLA.
OL,13,F"Patients should not be left feeling
OL,14,Ffrightened or uncertain about their
OL,15,Fcare. Where appointments have been
OL,16,Flost or delayed, the trust must act
OL,17,Fquickly to ensure that these are
OL,18,Frescheduled without undue wait.
